1
00:00:00,980 --> 00:00:04,860
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}SCHOOL FESTIVAL REPS
BOYS:
GIRLS:</b></font>

2
00:00:01,870 --> 00:00:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel so bad for the girls! 
Talk about rotten luck.</font>

3
00:00:04,860 --> 00:00:05,690
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}SCHOOL FESTIVAL REPS
BOYS: MAEHARA MAKI
GIRLS:</b></font>

4
00:00:05,690 --> 00:00:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoever wins has to babysit Maehara.</font>

5
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:10,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please... Please no.</font>

6
00:00:11,670 --> 00:00:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! I struck out!</font>

7
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay, struck out!</font>

8
00:00:17,060 --> 00:00:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Safe!</font>

9
00:00:27,550 --> 00:00:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you all hate Maehara-kun or something?</font>

10
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:34,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you acting like this?</font>

11
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you have to shun 
and exclude him so much?</font>

12
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He hasn't done anything wrong.</font>

13
00:00:41,050 --> 00:00:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So tell me why!</font>

14
00:00:44,350 --> 00:00:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, can I volunteer for the position?</font>

15
00:00:47,700 --> 00:00:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

16
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to work with Maehara-kun.</font>

17
00:00:52,020 --> 00:00:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean...</font>

18
00:00:53,410 --> 00:00:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd prefer to pick someone 
who actually wants to do it, too.</font>

19
00:00:57,370 --> 00:01:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay with that, Maehara-kun?</font>

20
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Amami-san says so, 
 I have no complaints.</font>

21
00:01:03,110 --> 00:01:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Sensei.</font>

22
00:01:04,710 --> 00:01:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won.</font>

23
00:01:09,130 --> 00:01:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

24
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Asanagi-san...</font>

25
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoever draws the winning lot gets 
the job. That's how it works, right?</font>

26
00:02:48,770 --> 00:02:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have the time, so I'll do it.</font>

27
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:54,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I said I'd do it—</font>

28
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Owwie.</font>

29
00:02:55,650 --> 00:02:58,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to calm down, Yuu.</font>

30
00:02:58,710 --> 00:03:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get that the way they were treating 
Maehara-kun ticked you off.</font>

31
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you took it a little too far.</font>

32
00:03:06,370 --> 00:03:07,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just take a look around.</font>

33
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, s-sorry, Umi. I...</font>

34
00:03:12,670 --> 00:03:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. I'm not the one 
you need to apologize to.</font>

35
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for acting out like that, everyone.</font>

36
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maehara-kun, I'm sorry for 
putting you on the spot, too.</font>

37
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:28,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm not bothered by it at all.</font>

38
00:03:29,730 --> 00:03:31,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, as per the results of the lottery,</font>

39
00:03:31,780 --> 00:03:36,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">our class reps for the festival will be 
Maehara Maki and me, Asanagi Umi.</font>

40
00:03:36,870 --> 00:03:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We look forward to your support, guys.</font>

41
00:03:39,990 --> 00:03:43,450
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}A/V ROOM</b></font>

42
00:03:40,490 --> 00:03:43,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, you're amazing, Asanagi.</font>

43
00:03:43,450 --> 00:03:47,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't I? Feel free to praise me more.</font>

44
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, now you're getting carried away.</font>

45
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though I guess I have to 
hand it to you this time.</font>

46
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuu's the one who's actually 
amazing, though.</font>

47
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:04,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She went at them straight up, 
not caring about ruining the vibes.</font>

48
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so cool that she can get angry 
on somebody's behalf like that.</font>

49
00:04:08,770 --> 00:04:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, it must've felt good 
when she yelled at the class, right?</font>

50
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meanwhile,</font>

51
00:04:17,470 --> 00:04:20,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I prioritize positive vibes over all else,</font>

52
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I could never do something like that.</font>

53
00:04:23,420 --> 00:04:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is everybody here?</font>

54
00:04:28,450 --> 00:04:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Seki, the student council president.</font>

55
00:04:30,820 --> 00:04:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get right down to business.</font>

56
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the first meeting of this year's 
school festival executive committee.</font>

57
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why did Asanagi sound a little down?</i></font>

58
00:04:39,490 --> 00:04:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess homeroom did turn 
into a mess over me.</i></font>

59
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I gotta do this and show everyone!</i></font>

60
00:04:48,550 --> 00:04:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi!</font>

61
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You waited for us? You didn't have to.</font>

62
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, but...</font>

63
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for today. Thanks so much.</font>

64
00:04:57,860 --> 00:05:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You waited for me just to say that?</font>

65
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

66
00:05:01,030 --> 00:05:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you hadn't stopped me, I...</font>

67
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would've said much nastier things.</font>

68
00:05:06,610 --> 00:05:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured.</font>

69
00:05:09,330 --> 00:05:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank <i>you</i>, actually.</font>

70
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

71
00:05:12,930 --> 00:05:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

72
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:15,500
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}WINNER</b></font>

73
00:05:18,350 --> 00:05:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who wants to see infighting when 
we're supposed to work as a team?</font>

74
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, right?</font>

75
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were my knight 
in shining armor back there.</font>

76
00:05:33,650 --> 00:05:36,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been ages since 
you've called me that.</font>

77
00:05:37,610 --> 00:05:40,070
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}DECOR</b></font>

78
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you have it.</font>

79
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our class has been put 
in charge of the decor.</font>

80
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

81
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop that.</font>

82
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit complaining just because 
we couldn't do a maid café.</font>

83
00:05:49,710 --> 00:05:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can be proactive and 
come up with decor ideas,</font>

84
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">some cosplay on the day might not be 
out of the realm of possibility.</font>

85
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

86
00:05:59,930 --> 00:06:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For Yuu and Nina, that is.</font>

87
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?!</font>

88
00:06:02,670 --> 00:06:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why just Ninacchi and me? What about you?</font>

89
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the producer this time.</font>

90
00:06:07,850 --> 00:06:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's imperative that we exploit you two 
to secure #1 on the popularity ranking.</font>

91
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that right, Maehara-kun?</font>

92
00:06:15,910 --> 00:06:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't ask me.</font>

93
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, anybody got any decor ideas?</font>

94
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

95
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do have an idea.</font>

96
00:06:31,510 --> 00:06:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go for it, Maehara-kun.</font>

97
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mosaic art using cans, huh?</font>

98
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:44,300
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}DECOR
EMPTY CAN MOSAIC ART</b></font>

99
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice going, Maehara. 
You actually thought this out.</font>

100
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That wore me out.</font>

101
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:49,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? That was only the first discussion.</font>

102
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad I'm working with you.</font>

103
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:58,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If this were Amami-san or someone else, 
my nerves would've given out midway.</font>

104
00:06:59,030 --> 00:07:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right? You should be 
thanking my lucky stars...</font>

105
00:07:03,690 --> 00:07:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is what I'd like to say...</font>

106
00:07:07,010 --> 00:07:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, a gift for you.</font>

107
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the lot I drew the other day.</font>

108
00:07:14,580 --> 00:07:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I actually didn't win.</font>

109
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You came up with that idea 
in the middle of that disaster?</font>

110
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:24,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really amazing.</font>

111
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you gonna tell me off? 
I cheated, you know?</font>

112
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd cheated people out of 
something they wanted, sure.</font>

113
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:36,190
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}WINNER</b></font>

114
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

115
00:07:36,710 --> 00:07:39,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you drew the winner.</font>

116
00:07:39,850 --> 00:07:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

117
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Maehara.</font>

118
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Color Sorting Minister Amami here!</font>

119
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Red ones go there! 
And yellow ones over here!</font>

120
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, I'm not happy with this.</font>

121
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:04,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ended up just copying the original.</font>

122
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:06,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is plenty impressive.</font>

123
00:08:06,340 --> 00:08:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we paint this in, pixelate it, 
and decide on a color scheme.</font>

124
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After that, we'll just have to punch holes
 in tons of cans and connect them.</font>

125
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi!</font>

126
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter, Color Sorting Minister?</font>

127
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reporting in!</font>

128
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have too many dirty cans with 
stuff like cigarette butts in them!</font>

129
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's put those aside and wash them later.</font>

130
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should probably wash out 
the sugary drink cans, too.</font>

131
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey, a manga.</font>

132
00:08:33,170 --> 00:08:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, can I try drawing this?</font>

133
00:08:42,590 --> 00:08:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Done!</font>

134
00:08:43,980 --> 00:08:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think? 
I just drew a pose I came up with.</font>

135
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amami-san... are you actually 
a pro illustrator in secret?</font>

136
00:08:52,890 --> 00:08:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, please! But I'm glad I drew something 
I'm happy with. It's been a while.</font>

137
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asanagi-san?</font>

138
00:09:00,590 --> 00:09:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-If she's this good, 
we should leave the art to Yuu.</font>

139
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure? But who'll be 
the Color Sorting Minister?</font>

140
00:09:09,330 --> 00:09:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can have Nina take over.</font>

141
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roger that!</font>

142
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi, Maki-kun! Let's do this!</font>

143
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

144
00:09:47,050 --> 00:09:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, this is crazy good!</font>

145
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuu drew that.</font>

146
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

147
00:09:52,530 --> 00:09:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She really <i>can</i> do it all.</font>

148
00:09:55,110 --> 00:09:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Other than study.</font>

149
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:04,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for cleaning up that mess 
during homeroom, Asanagi-chan.</font>

150
00:10:05,650 --> 00:10:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were too mean to Maehara-kun. 
We got carried away.</font>

151
00:10:10,140 --> 00:10:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course Yuu-chan would get angry.</font>

152
00:10:12,650 --> 00:10:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you hadn't stopped it there, 
we might've...</font>

153
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maehara's working his butt off, 
so help him out, okay?</font>

154
00:10:21,850 --> 00:10:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep.</font>

155
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya.</font>

156
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:32,110
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}GOOD WORK, ASANAGI</b></font>

157
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,610
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}PRAISE ME MORE</b></font>

158
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:35,110
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}ATTAGIRL</b></font>

159
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:37,820
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}DON'T FEEL PRESSURED TO COME OVER ON
FRIDAY. YOU CAN GO HOME AND REST UP.</b></font>

160
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This feels like a rarity these days.</font>

161
00:11:06,190 --> 00:11:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, for the love of...</font>

162
00:11:08,860 --> 00:11:10,650
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}KARAOKE CAN</b></font>

163
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it? What's up?</font>

164
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, sorry, are you out?</i></font>

165
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just felt like it wouldn't be right 
to make adjustments on my own.</font>

166
00:11:23,490 --> 00:11:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okay, and?</i></font>

167
00:11:25,970 --> 00:11:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, uh... if you feel like it...</font>

168
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh-huh?</i></font>

169
00:11:33,340 --> 00:11:39,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna come over for some food and games 
while we go over the design?</font>

170
00:11:39,850 --> 00:11:41,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or something?</i></font>

171
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So you're lonely without me around.</font>

172
00:11:45,900 --> 00:11:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's not what I'm saying.</i></font>

173
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't lie to me. I see right through you.</font>

174
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:53,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, just spit it out.</font>

175
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I, Maehara Maki, am currently 
missing Asanagi Umi to death!"</i></font>

176
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wrong! 
Fine, I'll just do this by myself!</font>

177
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye!</font>

178
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, wait.</i></font>

179
00:12:06,930 --> 00:12:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On second thought, can I come over?</i></font>

180
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:13,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kind of miss you, too.</font>

181
00:12:15,050 --> 00:12:17,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi? Is something the matter?</font>

182
00:12:17,340 --> 00:12:20,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, something came up at home.</font>

183
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:21,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna head out.</font>

184
00:12:22,310 --> 00:12:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

185
00:12:28,610 --> 00:12:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heya.</font>

186
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heya. Come on in.</font>

187
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Maehara.</font>

188
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:35,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

189
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just felt like saying it.</font>

190
00:12:38,530 --> 00:12:39,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck?</font>

191
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:45,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you've made a lot of progress.</font>

192
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really sorry for summoning you 
out of the blue.</font>

193
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:57,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I lie down for a bit?</font>

194
00:12:57,430 --> 00:13:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. You can take a nap if you want, too.</font>

195
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to take a nap? Here?</font>

196
00:13:04,230 --> 00:13:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone's</i> being quite daring.</font>

197
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you slept just fine the other day!</font>

198
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's okay.</font>

199
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Masaki-san's given me permission to 
kick your ass if you try anything funny.</font>

200
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh, that mother of mine.</font>

201
00:13:27,050 --> 00:13:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Maehara.</font>

202
00:13:28,990 --> 00:13:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

203
00:13:34,560 --> 00:13:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, I think I...</font>

204
00:13:39,310 --> 00:13:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

205
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amami-san?</font>

206
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good evening, Maki-kun. 
Sorry for showing up so late.</font>

207
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi? I know you're there.</font>

208
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come in first.</font>

209
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:04,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. I won't stay long.</font>

210
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to intrude 
on your alone time.</font>

211
00:14:08,330 --> 00:14:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, Yuu. I wasn't trying to...</font>

212
00:14:11,100 --> 00:14:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amami-san.</font>

213
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did you figure us out?</font>

214
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:21,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'd been making a lot of excuses lately,
and she seemed oddly comfortable here.</font>

215
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:27,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi, why didn't you tell me 
you were hanging out with Maki-kun?</font>

216
00:14:27,470 --> 00:14:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

217
00:14:29,180 --> 00:14:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, it's my fault.</font>

218
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked her to keep it a secret.</font>

219
00:14:34,260 --> 00:14:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi.</font>

220
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that true?</font>

221
00:14:38,350 --> 00:14:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why won't you say anything? 
Do you not trust me?</font>

222
00:14:43,270 --> 00:14:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I the only one who thinks of us 
as best friends?</font>

223
00:14:46,420 --> 00:14:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you not see me as that?</font>

224
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it!</font>

225
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why?</font>

226
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

227
00:14:52,830 --> 00:14:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi!</font>

228
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:58,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad we're in the same class again!</font>

229
00:14:58,710 --> 00:15:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's so pretty. 
Like a model or something.</font>

230
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could brag about being friends 
with someone like that.</font>

231
00:15:05,060 --> 00:15:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, are you free next weekend?</font>

232
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry. I have plans.</font>

233
00:15:12,590 --> 00:15:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too.</font>

234
00:15:13,430 --> 00:15:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Umi-chan.</font>

235
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All good.</font>

236
00:15:18,780 --> 00:15:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over here, Yuu-chan!</font>

237
00:15:23,110 --> 00:15:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry! Did you wait long?</font>

238
00:15:26,330 --> 00:15:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Took you long enough.</font>

239
00:15:30,580 --> 00:15:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the one thing I can't tell you.</font>

240
00:15:32,830 --> 00:15:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to.</font>

241
00:15:34,490 --> 00:15:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maehara, sorry I got you mixed up in this.</font>

242
00:15:39,270 --> 00:15:41,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be heading out now.</font>

243
00:15:41,670 --> 00:15:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Umi! I'll go with you!</font>

244
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please let me go by myself.</font>

245
00:15:47,020 --> 00:15:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Yuu. I'm such a jerk.</font>

246
00:15:53,890 --> 00:15:55,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do I do, Maki-kun?</font>

247
00:15:56,310 --> 00:15:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen Umi like that.</font>

248
00:16:01,060 --> 00:16:04,520
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}< ASANAGI</b></font>

249
00:16:01,060 --> 00:16:03,070
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}AMAMI-SAN LEFT

HELLO?</b></font>

250
00:16:03,070 --> 00:16:04,530
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}HELLO?

ASANAGI?</b></font>

251
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:06,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She read them, but she didn't respond.</i></font>

252
00:16:06,810 --> 00:16:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's not going to skip school, right?</i></font>

253
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning.</font>

254
00:16:11,910 --> 00:16:13,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, Maki-kun.</font>

255
00:16:13,650 --> 00:16:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, Amami-san.
 And Asanagi-san, too.</font>

256
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

257
00:16:19,790 --> 00:16:21,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She seems the same as usual.</i></font>

258
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:25,840
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}TODAY
MAKI-KUN, SORRY ABOUT THIS</b></font>

259
00:16:24,340 --> 00:16:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Amami-san?</i></font>

260
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Um, so it's about Umi. 
Have you talked to her since?</i></font>

261
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, I haven't. How about you?</i></font>

262
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Me neither, actually.</i></font>

263
00:16:41,190 --> 00:16:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I felt too awkward to reach out to her.</i></font>

264
00:16:44,540 --> 00:16:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But she came to pick me up on Monday 
morning like nothing happened,</i></font>

265
00:16:49,060 --> 00:16:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I thought maybe you'd 
smoothed things over with her.</i></font>

266
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did she say anything?</i></font>

267
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Sorry about Friday. Forget about it."</i></font>

268
00:16:58,300 --> 00:16:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's it.</i></font>

269
00:17:01,190 --> 00:17:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I had my hands full just keeping Asanagi 
and my secret under wraps.</i></font>

270
00:17:06,450 --> 00:17:08,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the one thing I can't tell you.</font>

271
00:17:08,580 --> 00:17:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to.</font>

272
00:17:10,010 --> 00:17:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if Asanagi had to deal with 
all that </i>and<i> a secret of her own?</i></font>

273
00:17:14,780 --> 00:17:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if she had to bear 
that burden all by herself?</i></font>

274
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ninacchi, no problems with squad B?</font>

275
00:17:19,990 --> 00:17:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, I think we're a bit short on reds.</font>

276
00:17:23,370 --> 00:17:25,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we get everybody 
together to drink Core Cola?</font>

277
00:17:27,120 --> 00:17:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A... Asanagi-san.</font>

278
00:17:30,100 --> 00:17:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a sec?</font>

279
00:17:31,340 --> 00:17:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

280
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:37,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got something 
important to say to you.</font>

281
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:43,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, I need to stay here 
to give out instructions.</font>

282
00:17:43,020 --> 00:17:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be fine. We're checking 
the design as we work.</font>

283
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can go, Umi.</font>

284
00:17:50,150 --> 00:17:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squad B will be fine 
without you reps around, too.</font>

285
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me, Asanagi.</font>

286
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You idiot! You stupid idiot!</font>

287
00:18:01,230 --> 00:18:04,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's supposed to be a secret 
that we're friends!</font>

288
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:07,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you tied my hands 
by asking in front of everybody!</font>

289
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's your fault for leaving me on read.</font>

290
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:14,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, I mean, I...</font>

291
00:18:14,810 --> 00:18:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, let's get the work 
out of the way first.</font>

292
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That goes in black.</font>

293
00:18:28,630 --> 00:18:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Maehara.</font>

294
00:18:30,950 --> 00:18:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

295
00:18:33,270 --> 00:18:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you gonna ask?</font>

296
00:18:35,170 --> 00:18:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About what?</font>

297
00:18:36,450 --> 00:18:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why I've been avoiding you, 
and all that other stuff.</font>

298
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you wanna talk about it?</font>

299
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't...</font>

300
00:18:44,690 --> 00:18:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I know this can't go on forever.</font>

301
00:18:49,430 --> 00:18:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thing with Yuu, too.</font>

302
00:18:51,860 --> 00:18:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frankly, I do wanna ask, and I do 
wanna know what you're thinking.</font>

303
00:18:58,600 --> 00:19:01,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm not going to force it out of you.</font>

304
00:19:01,540 --> 00:19:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure? I might not ever tell you.</font>

305
00:19:05,870 --> 00:19:09,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's fine, too. 
I'll wait until you're ready.</font>

306
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:15,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maehara, you dumbass.</font>

307
00:19:15,910 --> 00:19:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what?</font>

308
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You stupid idiot!</font>

309
00:19:20,980 --> 00:19:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like how nice you are, but when you 
take that too far, you're just a softie!</font>

310
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And some nasty person might 
take advantage of you someday.</font>

311
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A nasty coward like me, for example.</font>

312
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Uh...</font>

313
00:19:35,540 --> 00:19:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't! You're not allowed to turn around!</font>

314
00:19:40,750 --> 00:19:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Maehara.</font>

315
00:19:42,890 --> 00:19:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I said I wanted to fess up, 
would you hear me out?</font>

316
00:19:48,250 --> 00:19:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would.</font>

317
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, could I ask you to wait 
until after the school festival?</font>

318
00:19:54,850 --> 00:19:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's up to you.</font>

319
00:19:58,030 --> 00:19:59,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

320
00:20:00,770 --> 00:20:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll hash it out with Yuu, too. 
So just give me some time.</font>

321
00:20:06,210 --> 00:20:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

322
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:09,440
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}JOUTOU HIGH SCHOOL FESTIVAL</b></font>

323
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:12,110
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}JOUTOU HIGH SCHOOL FESTIVAL</b></font>

324
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:17,900
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}JOUTOU HIGH SCHOOL FESTIVAL</b></font>

325
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

326
00:20:33,850 --> 00:20:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even I could pull it off, huh?</font>

327
00:20:37,050 --> 00:20:37,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

328
00:20:40,630 --> 00:20:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asanagi, can I ask you for something?</font>

329
00:20:45,790 --> 00:20:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't want to, that's fine.</font>

330
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But can we hold hands?</font>

331
00:20:53,230 --> 00:20:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's just... 
It seemed like you were cold.</font>

332
00:20:58,390 --> 00:21:02,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you trying to lift my spirits?</font>

333
00:21:03,470 --> 00:21:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You? Looking out for me?</font>

334
00:21:07,090 --> 00:21:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your hand's so warm.</font>

335
00:21:09,140 --> 00:21:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gee, thanks.</font>

336
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks. That helped me relax some.</font>

337
00:21:16,570 --> 00:21:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're late, Yuu.</font>

338
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Umi. I got too into 
talking to some friends.</font>

339
00:21:23,430 --> 00:21:24,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

340
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over here, you two!</font>

341
00:21:28,210 --> 00:21:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, we need to introduce them to Maki-kun.</font>

342
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umi and I have been friends 
with them since elementary school.</font>

343
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wrong, Yuu.</font>

344
00:21:36,890 --> 00:21:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That may be true for you,</font>

345
00:21:39,130 --> 00:21:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's not for me.</font>

346
00:21:41,820 --> 00:21:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, you two don't really 
see me as a friend, do you?</font>

347
00:21:50,700 --> 00:21:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asanagi...</font>

348
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is sooner than I planned,</font>

349
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but hear me out, Maehara and Yuu.</font>

350
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me tell you about my petty 
little inferiority complex.</font>

351
00:22:07,140 --> 00:22:10,810
